# ✅ **5. Packet Lifecycle Diagram (Mermaid Sequence)**

```markdown
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant NIC as NIC
    participant CAP as AF_PACKET Capture
    participant DET as Protocol Detector
    participant PAR as Parser
    participant ML as ML Engine
    participant OUT as Alert/Stats

    NIC->>CAP: Raw Ethernet frame
    CAP->>DET: Pass payload
    DET->>PAR: Dispatch to protocol parser
    PAR->>ML: Extract features (optional)
    ML->>OUT: Suspicion score
    PAR->>OUT: Flags, domain, URI
    OUT->>OUT: Log alert + update counters
